                "institute": "1USATAM"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Triga reactor with a very fast",
                " pneumatic transfer system"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Fast fission neutron spectrum in a pool-type reactor",
                "using a fast flux irradiation device. This device was",
                "characterized using a foil activation technique."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 10B-F3 proportional counter. The detector array",
                "was calibrated using a energy response function,",
                "calculated by the MCNP code. This response function was",
                "used to adjust the measured efficiency of the array for",
                "the Cf-252 calibration source to that expected for",
                "delay neutron."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ANALYSIS": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Yields and decay constants were acquired from the",
                "measured emission rates using a graphical stripping",
                "procedure, then they were improved using a least",
                "squares technique."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrected for detector dead-time"
              ]
            }
          ],
